OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FThe use of so-called "forever
OL,7,Fchemicals" in everyday items such as
OL,8,Fcookware and school uniforms should be
OL,9,Fphased out, amid growing concerns over
OL,10,Ftheir impact on health and nature, MPs
OL,11,Fhave said.
OL,13,FThe cross-party Environmental Audit
OL,14,FCommittee (EAC) is calling on the
OL,15,Fgovernment to restrict all non-
OL,16,Fessential uses of Perfluoroalkyl and
OL,17,FPolyfluoroalkyl Substances ` or PFAs `
OL,18,Fin consumer products from 2027.
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
