PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FPFAs are called "forever chemicals"
OL,7,Fbecause they can take centuries to
OL,8,Fbreak down in the environment. They
OL,9,Fare widely used across industries and
OL,10,Fin products, including non-stick pans,
OL,11,Ffirefighting foams, pesticides,
OL,12,Fcosmetics and medical devices.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FBut growing evidence shows they pose
OL,7,Frisks to both people and planet,
OL,8,Faccumulating in the bodies of living
OL,9,Forganisms and potentially leading to
OL,10,Fsevere health conditions, including
OL,11,Fcancer and fertility issues.
OL,13,FIn a report published on Thursday
OL,14,Ffollowing an inquiry into PFAs, the
OL,15,Fgroup of MPs said ministers must take
OL,16,Fa stronger approach to regulating the
OL,17,Fharmful toxins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FThe EAC also wants the government to
OL,7,Fintroduce a "polluter pays" principle
OL,8,Fwhere businesses responsible for PFAs
OL,9,Fseeping into waterways and soil pay
OL,10,Ffor the clean up, and to establish a
OL,11,Fnational fund for remediation and
OL,12,Finvest in technologies that can
OL,13,Fdestroy the toxins safely.
OL,15,F"PFAs are now central to everyday and
OL,16,Fsome lifesaving products, and nearly
OL,17,Fall of us will have some level of PFAs
OL,18,Fin our bodies," said EAC chairman Toby
OL,19,FPerkins.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@[O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,F"But evidence we heard throughout our
OL,7,Finquiry suggests that our dependence
OL,8,Fon PFAs has come with a cost to the
OL,9,Fenvironment, and perhaps to human
OL,10,Fhealth too."
OL,12,FIn February, the government published
OL,13,Fa PFAs action plan, outlining measures
OL,14,Fthat ministers, businesses and
OL,15,Fregulators can take to better
OL,16,Funderstand how the chemicals spread
OL,17,Finto the environment, and how to
OL,18,Freduce public and environmental
OL,19,Fexposure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FBut campaigners were quick to
OL,7,Fcriticise the government for not
OL,8,Fconsidering a ban or restrictions on
OL,9,Ftheir use, as the European Union and
OL,10,FCalifornia have done.
OL,12,FMr Perkins said the committee welcomed
OL,13,Fthe government's plan but that it
OL,14,F"does not go far enough".
OL,16,F"It appears to be a plan to eventually
OL,17,Fhave a plan, rather than a concrete
OL,18,Fset of commitments to reduce and
OL,19,Fremediate PFAs," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@XO]xD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FThe committee said that ministers
OL,7,Fshould introduce interim limits on
OL,8,Flevels found in consumer products
OL,9,Fstill on the market and standardised
OL,10,Flabelling to inform consumers about
OL,11,Fthe chemicals present.
OL,13,FIt also said that companies should get
OL,14,Fapproval before introducing newly
OL,15,Fdeveloped PFAs, rather than the
OL,16,Fgovernment waiting for proof that a
OL,17,Fchemical is harmful before it is
OL,18,Fbanned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FThe committee also argued that without
OL,7,Frestricting "groups" of these
OL,8,Fchemicals, the government risks taking
OL,9,Fa "whack-a-mole" approach to
OL,10,Fregulation.
OL,12,FElsewhere, the report said that
OL,13,Fvoluntary action on these chemicals
OL,14,Fand self-regulation by industry is not
OL,15,Fsufficient to reduce PFA emissions.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@TO]qD@COUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
