OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776960675
OL,3,CRestrict 'forever chemicals' that hurt
OL,4,Cpeople and planet, MPs urge
OL,6,FWhile the EAC welcomed the
OL,7,Fgovernment's recent proposals to set
OL,8,Flimits for levels found in drinking
OL,9,Fwater, it said significant gaps remain
OL,10,Fin limiting exposure to PFAs through
OL,11,Ffood and agriculture.
OL,13,FThe MPs are therefore calling for
OL,14,Flimits on the levels and types of PFAs
OL,15,Fpermitted in food.
OL,17,FITV News has contacted the Environment
OL,18,FDepartment (Defra) for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
